title: #15 Dana Loesch Rips Feminists, Kira Davis Rips Starbucks, And I RIP FunDip!
description:
This week we're joined by two STRONG, Conservative women.  First up, Dana Loesch tells us about her upbringing as a liberal, her transition into Conservatism, and just why becoming a mom has caused her to loathe feminists!
Then we have Kira Davis, a strong, Black woman who absolutely tears Starbucks a new one, in an epic interview that must be heard to be believed.
